"```sql\nSELECT c.Text\nFROM comments c\nJOIN posts p ON c.PostId = p.Id\nJOIN postHistory ph ON ph.PostId = p.Id\nWHERE p.Title = 'Why square the difference instead of taking the absolute value in standard deviation?'\nAND ph.UserId = c.UserId;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the text of comments from users who have edited the post with the specified title. It joins the `comments`, `posts`, and `postHistory` tables to ensure that the comments are from users who have edited the post."